=== AMASHURI YIZE ===
'''Emma Claudine''' yaminuje muri [[Kaminuza y'u Rwanda]] mu itangazamakuru (2000-2004). Afite impamyabumenyi y'icyiciro cya gatatu cya Kaminuza yakuye mu gihugu cya Cyprus (Republic of Cyprus)<ref>https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cyprus</ref>  muri [https://www.unic.ac.cy/ University of Nicosia] mu bijyanye no gucunga imishinga (Business Administration and Management General). Afite ubumenyi mu bijyanye na filime ndetse mu 2008 yasoje amasomo ye mu [[Ubuholandi|Buholandi]]. <ref>https://inyarwanda.com/inkuru/112566/emma-claudine-yahawe-akazi-muri-biro-byumuvugizi-wa-guverinoma-112566.html</ref>

===== IMIRIMO YAKOZE =====
Emma Claudine Nyuma y'igihe kinini akorera Radio Salus ya [[Kaminuza y'u Rwanda|Kaminiza y'u Rwanda]] ishami rya Huye,riri mu [[Akarere ka Huye]], aho ibiganiro byinshi muri byo byibandaga kubuzima bw'imyororokere, akaba yarakoraga kandi noguteza imbere imyidagaduro mu [[Rwanda]] cyane muri muzika, aho yari umuyobozi wa Ikirezi Group itegura ikanatanga ibihembo bya Salax Awards.<ref>https://inyarwanda.com/inkuru/58523/nyuma-y-igihe-kinini-yari-ahamaze-emma-claudine-ntakiri-umunyamakuru-wa-radio-salus-58523.html</ref> Yaje kuhava muri 2014 agiye gukora muri NGOs yitwa Girl Hub Rwanda itegura ikinyamakuru ni Nyampinga.<ref>https://inyarwanda.com/inkuru/83066/urubyiruko-rukina-ikinamico-ya-ninyampinga-sakwe-rwahsyize-h-83066.html</ref> <ref>http://ninyampinga.com/en/</ref><ref>https://www.global.girleffect.org/what-we-do/youth-brands/ni-nyampinga/</ref><ref>https://www.isimbi.rw/imyidagaduro/article/emma-claudine-wakoreye-radio-salus-yahawe-umwanya-n-inama-y-abaminisitiri</ref>Avuye mu buholandei yasangije ubumenyi itsinda rya Les Stars Theatre muri Kminuza y'uRwanda i butare n'abandi banyamakuru ba Radio Salus banandika ikinamico.

'''Emma Claudine''' amaze imyaka 15 afatwa nka "'''Shangazi'''" w'ingimbi n'abangavu kubera ibiganiro kubera ibiganiro byerekeye ubuzima bw'imyororokere, iyi gahunda akaba yarayitangiriye kuri Radio Salus mu kiganiro yise "IMENYE NAWE" mu mwaka 2005. yabaye kandi Program Manager wa Radio Salus,<ref>https://onlineradiobox.com/rw/salus/</ref> mu gihe cy'imyaka 9 n'amezi 5.Yakoze ikiganiro cyiswe "BAZA SHANGAZI" mu kinyamakuru 'NI NYAMPINGA"<ref>https://inyarwanda.com/inkuru/83066/urubyiruko-rukina-ikinamico-ya-ninyampinga-sakwe-rwahsyize-h-83066.html</ref><ref>https://inyarwanda.com/inkuru/83066/urubyiruko-rukina-ikinamico-ya-ninyampinga-sakwe-rwahsyize-h-83066.html</ref><ref>https://www.global.girleffect.org/what-we-do/youth-brands/ni-nyampinga/</ref> yari anabereye Managing Editor".<ref>https://www.global.girleffect.org/what-we-do/youth-brands/ni-nyampinga/</ref> <ref>http://ninyampinga.com/en/</ref>Akaba yaramaze imyaka 5 akuriye itumanaho mu kigo cy'abanyamerika gishinzwe iterambere mpuzamahanga ('''USAID'''). Yari asazwe akuriye itumanaho muri RwandaEquip umushinga wa Bridge international Academies ugamije guteza imbere uburezi mu [[Rwanda]].<ref>https://rwandaequip.org.rw/</ref> Yabaye umwe mu bagize Inama y'ubutegetsi mu inama nkuru y'itagazamakuru bigenzura ('''RMC'''). Yamaze imyaka 3 ari umunyamabanga mu ishyirahamwe ry'ubanyamakuru b'abagore ('''ARFEM''').<ref>http://www.rwandajournalists.com/membership/arj-affiliates/article/arfem</ref> Yanamaze umwaka umwe n'umezi abiri akuriye itumanaho muri Catholic Relief Services.<ref>https://www.crs.org/</ref> Ni umwe mu bari bagize Akanama Nkemurampaka kemeje abakobwa 37 batsinze ijonjora rya Miss Rwanda 2021. Ubu '''Emma Claudine''' yahawe ishingano nshya yagizwe umusesenguzi mu by'itumanaho mu biro by'Umuvugizi wa Guverinema y'u [[Rwanda]].<ref>https://inyarwanda.com/inkuru/112566/emma-claudine-yahawe-akazi-muri-biro-byumuvugizi-wa-guverinoma-112566.html</ref> 

